data.description: Welcome to your dream home 13719 Greenway Drive, a home where comfort meets elegance. Nestled in the heart of Sugar Land, TX, this beautifully remodeled, fully-furnished 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is waiting for you to call it home. This home features a gourmet kitchen equipped with modern appliances - a haven for your culinary adventures. All appliances and high-quality furniture are included in the purchase, making the move a breeze. The outdoor space is a private oasis complete with a stunning pool, perfect for Texas summers. Located in a family-friendly community, this home is a stone's throw away from top-rated schools, fine dining, shopping, and vibrant parks. While you'll enjoy the small-town charm of Sugar Land, you'll also appreciate the easy access to the bustling city of Houston. Don't miss this unique opportunity - a fully furnished, move-in-ready home in a thriving community. Your dream home at 13719 Greenway Drive is waiting for you! Schedule a showing today.
